Emacs X Input Method
====================

EXIM (Emacs X Input Method) is an X input method server utilizing Emacs as its
backend. Please refer to "exim.el" for more details.

EXIM is mainly designed for working with EXWM window manger:
  + EXWM: https://github.com/ch11ng/exwm

EXIM is built on top of XELB and its utility libraris:
  + XELB: https://github.com/ch11ng/xelb
  + XELB utilility libraries: https://github.com/ch11ng/xelb-util
